   UserRole.Text,
   "Admin", "Welcome Admin!",
   "Manager", "Welcome Manager!",
   "Employee", "Welcome Employee!",
   "Role not recognized"
)
ğŸ‘‰ If the UserRole is "Manager", it will return "Welcome Manager!".
